<h4 id="1-4-4-resize-text-aa"><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-scale.html">1.4.4 Resize text (AA)</a></h4>
<p>It must be possible for people to increase the size of text by up to 200%. This ensures that partially sighted people can comfortably read content.</p>
<h5 id="requirements-what-to-do">Requirements / What to do?</h5>

<ul>
<li>  We need to decide whether we want to use text resize or zoom as the preferred mechanism.</li>
</ul>
